This has been the wildest and most rewarding year of my life, both personal=
ly and professionally: our son, Dev, turned 6 months old yesterday, and Not=
 Boring turned one on Friday.=C2=A0
A year ago, we knew that Dev was coming, but I had no idea what I was going=
