y lockdowns (and was probably a bad idea anyway), and to top it off, I caug=
ht COVID the week I decided to start writing Not Boring. I was lost.=C2=A0
Somehow, since then, with all of your help, I=E2=80=99ve built my dream job=
=2E Over the past 365 days, I=E2=80=99ve:
Written and sent 417k words. That=E2=80=99s more than all seven Chronicles =
of Narnia.=C2=A0
