Run a syndicate which has invested nearly $2 million in fourteen companies.=
=C2=A0
Generated more revenue than I=E2=80=99ve ever made in a full-time job.=C2=
=A0
I legitimately didn=E2=80=99t believe this was possible. I would see people=
 with big followings on Twitter or big subscriber lists and think that they=
