oment.=C2=A0
Today, I want to share the Not Boring story as honestly as possible -- it o=
ften looks way easier from the outside -- with lessons I=E2=80=99ve learned=
 on writing, growth, business models, investing, and creator psychology spr=
inkled in. We=E2=80=99ll cover:
