ategy, finance, economics, and tech -- even though they were crowded, as lo=
ng as I wrote about it with my own, unique voice.=C2=A0
That was a huge unlock, and a lesson in counter-positioning. Counter-positi=
oning, my favorite of Hamilton Helmer=E2=80=99s 7 Powers [https://email.mg2=
=2Esubstack.com/c/eJxFkMtuhDAMRb9msgPlQQ=
hZZNEuZl2pH4BC4pmJBhKURxH9-gZYVLJsydf=
WtY_RGZ4h7moNKaMjjXlfQXnY0gw5Q0QlQRydVaSnA-OdRFZ1lgx8QC6NjwiwaDerHAugtUyzMz=
