><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 =
0 1em 0;">This has been the wildest and most rewarding year of my life, bot=
h personally and professionally: our son, Dev, turned 6 months old yesterda=
y, and Not Boring turned one on Friday.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a=
; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">A year ago, we kn=
ew that Dev was coming, but I had no idea what I was going to do. I had qui=
t my job, launched an in-person company that got crushed by lockdowns (and =
was probably a bad idea anyway), and to top it off, I caught COVID the week=
 I decided to start writing Not Boring. I was lost.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"co=
lor: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Someh=
ow, since then, with all of your help, I&#8217;ve built my dream job. Over =
the past 365 days, I&#8217;ve:</p><ul style=3D"margin: 1em 0;"><li style=3D=
"margin: 3.75px 0 3.75px 7.5px; mso-special-format: bullet;"><p style=3D"co=
lor: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;">Written and s=
ent <strong>417k words</strong>. That&#8217;s more than all seven <em>Chron=
icles of Narnia</em>.&nbsp;</p></li><li style=3D"margin: 3.75px 0 3.75px 7.=
5px; mso-special-format: bullet;"><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16=
px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;">Grown from under 500 subscribers to <str=
ong>over 42,000</strong>.</p></li><li style=3D"margin: 3.75px 0 3.75px 7.5p=
x; mso-special-format: bullet;"><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px=
; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;">Run a syndicate which has <strong>invested=
 nearly $2 million</strong> in fourteen companies.&nbsp;</p></li><li style=
=3D"margin: 3.75px 0 3.75px 7.5px; mso-special-format: bullet;"><p style=3D=
"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;">Generated =
<strong>more revenue than I&#8217;ve ever made in a full-time job</strong>.=
&nbsp;</p></li></ul><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-heigh=
t: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">I legitimately didn&#8217;t believe this was p=
